    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You've got to see this absolute beauty. It\u2019s been pampered since day one and honestly looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor! Super clean, drives like a dream, and it's ready for its next adventure with you. If you're looking for something that's been kept in truly flawless shape, this is the one! Come take a look\u2014you're going to love it!",
