    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade BMW E46 M3, featuring the naturally aspirated S54 3.2L inline-six equipped with individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. This example is mechanically superlative: the rod bearing service is documented, the VANOS system has been overhauled with upgraded seals, and the rear subframe has been proactively reinforced with a structural plate kit. Power is routed through a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission to a GKN-sourced limited-slip differential, providing exceptional mechanical grip and linear torque delivery. The chassis remains taut, utilizing factory-spec bushings and Bilstein dampers to maintain original steering feedback and lateral stability. The exterior finish displays remarkable depth with no evidence of clear coat failure or track-use pitting. This is a turn-key specimen for the purist seeking the zenith of the analog M-car era.",
      "price": 48500.0,
